title: Fahmi Rizaldi
text:
Hi! I am Fahmi (파흐미). I am a Master Student at the Pusan National University, majoring in Computer Science.
Currently I am working as a Research Student under Professor Kwon Joonho at the Data Science Laboratory.
My research is about Anomaly Detection.
